article_text:
One Democrat is challenging U.S. Rep. Marc Veasey

Two Republicans are in the race as well

At stake is a two-year term that pays $174,000 a year

article_metadata.news-keywords: Texas, 33rd Congressional District, Marc Veasey, Carlos Quintanilla, Bruce Chadwick, M. Mark Mitchell
article_metadata.description: The quest to represent the 33rd Congressional District has been a battle between Dallas and Fort Worth, Democrat and Republican, even black and Hispanic, since it was first created.
